import sys
k, x = list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split()))
for i in range(k):
    print(x - k + 1 + i, end=" ")

import sys

n = int(sys.stdin.readline())
arr = []
for i in range(n):
    arr.append(list(map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())))

for i in range(n):
    print(arr[i])

import sys

k, x = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().split())

for i in range(max(x - k + 1, -1000000), min(x + k, 1000000) + 1):
    print(i, end=' ')
